        <type name="String"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>If booking is in a  controlled reefer environment. Is either true or false.

If the cargo has oxygen or carbon dioxide levels set, or has a curtain it has a controlled atmosphere.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
